Package: surveyreport
Type: Package
Title: Automatic Reports in Office Format Based on Tidy Specifications
Version: 0.0.0.9003
Author: Stephan Daus
Maintainer: Stephan Daus <stephus.daus@gmail.com>
	Description: A set of functions to read and process labelled data from survey services (currently SurveyXact is supported. UiO Nettskjema, SurveyMonkey and Opinio later). Produces highly customizable figures, text, analyses and reports for a batch of possible dpendent-independent relations of possible interest.
